title: Youxia Zhanji
overview: Follows aspiring young Hou Mo who stimulated the potential of his genes in an accident, from a small character in the market to a knight who helps the weak. He overcomes his own shortcomings, surpasses himself, and gradually grows into a responsible and responsible new youth. With a group of partners with the same special talents, the "Range League", and the evil organization "The Ferryman", they fought wits and courage, and completed their mission of justice as a member of the Ranger League.
